name: Marina S.
headline: Project Manager | PRINCE2 Certified | Agile & Scrum Practitioner | Engineering Background (QA) | Expertise in Compliance and Software Development
creator: False
bio:
As a project manager with 4 years of experience, I am convinced that the success of a project directly depends on effective team management. My approach is based on understanding the value of each team member, the ability to find motivation, and inspire. 

I am supported in this by professional education in coaching, certification in project management (PRINCE2), and knowledge of Agile and Scrum methodologies. My technical background‚Äîa degree in software testing engineering‚Äîallows me to speak the same language as the development team and understand how the IT product lifecycle is structured.

name: Sergey Mardanov
headline: Business Development | Sales & Marketing | IR | Strategy | IT | EdTech | Aerospace
creator: False
current_position: Deputy CEO, Business Development & Investor Relations
past_company_2: Digital Education (JV of VK and Rostelecom), platform "Sferum" (www.sferum.ru )
bio:
Over the past 18 years of experience, I have held various positions in the field of technology entrepreneurship. This includes the creation of 25 university spin-off companies, the development of more than 100 university innovation ecosystems, and the promotion of digital and EdTech services to over 25 million users worldwide. Currently, I am involved in an aerospace startup, where I am applying all my knowledge, skills, and connections to business development, fundraising, sales scaling, and the development of a wide range of high-tech products under the SR Space holding company. In just one year, we brought the company to a pre-IPO on the MOEX over-the-counter market, with an estimated $17 million.

My passion lies in large-scale projects, particularly those that are HighTech or related with IT and Education. I am always open to new challenges and opportunities, particularly when there is a challenge, a talented team, and a global vision. 

I am a born communicator, salesman and assertive leader who enjoys generating ideas, who enjoys generating ideas, finding solutions, motivating people and being –∞ conflict solver. I enjoy a variety of active sports, including triathlon, snowboarding, surfing, and racket sports. I have taught more than one million children and visited more than 200 university campuses worldwide. I devote a special amount of time to raising my two adopted sons.
